  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT11">
<l>paṭṭuṭukku mayarttiraṅkum pāvai pēṇāḷ</l>
<l>paṉineṭuṅkaṇ ṇīrtatumpap paḷḷi koḷḷāḷ</l>
<l>eṭṭuṉaippō teṉkuṭaṅkā lirukka killā</l>
<l>ḷemperumāṉ tiruvaraṅka meṅkē yeṉṉum</l>
<l>maṭṭuvikki maṇivaṇṭu muraluṅ kūntal</l>
<l>maṭamāṉai yituceytār tammai meyyē</l>
<l>kaṭṭuvicci colleṉṉac coṉṉāḷ naṅkāy</l>
<l>kaṭalvaṇṇa rituceytār kāppā rārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Neglecting the clothes that she wears, [this] girl, who weeps, cares not;</l>
<l rend="indent">she does not sleep as the tears of [her] elongated, moist eyes overflow.</l>
<l>She who cannot sit on my lap for the tiniest length of time,</l>
<l rend="indent">keeps asking, “Where is Tiruvaraṅkam of our Lord?”</l>
<l>As a soothsayer said words truthfully to us [of] who did this</l>
<l rend="indent">to [this] simple girl with tresses where jewel[-like] bees hum, choking on nectar,</l>
<l>She said, “O Ladies, the sea-hued one did this.</l>
<l rend="indent">Who will protect her [now]?”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
